desc: An all Australian brand making homemade, oven baked, all organic dog treats. Our selection of Aussie puppy food are all natural, healthy and wheat free making them perfect for the sensitive tum of a pooch. Our pet treats are home baked and vegan, being a plant based dog food recipe makes P&N a healthy alternative

layout.text: ALL ORGANIC, NO NASTIES, GUILT-FREE DOG TREATS
made with only the finest organic, human-grade ingredients, our treats are a guilt-free way to treat your pup! being plant based and wheat free they are also gentle on a dogs tum.
